title: A Concise Course in Algebraic Topology - May JP
description:
Algebraic Topology is essential for doing advanced work in geometry, topology, 

differential geometry, algebraic geometry and lie groups. This book provides visual

intuition and concrete fundamentals into the subject. Great book if your first 

exposure to the subject.


Happy Learning!
